title: Ranking Every American Horror Story Season From Worst to Best
author: EJ Moreno
comment: 1984 was so much fun! It’s going in my #3 favorite spot, but #6 best season (Coven is my favorite, Asylum is best.)

description:
Any AHS fan will tell you that ranking the seasons is no easy task. You think you know what will place where, and by the end, you are spiraling like you're in the Murder House. Timestamps below for all my personal ranking of American Horror Story seasons, from worst to best.
